{"tid":2081479,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Gphone: 我深知正式選舉時，自己的名字出現在選票上的機會十分渺茫","createTime":"2020-06-27T09:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T09:22:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2ced453d18bd11fa5bcfe93f93cd4654d09ceb","tid":2081479,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:04:14.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒 Joshua Wong<br />\n【不屈火苗 存亡號召】<br />\n<br />\n我深知正式選舉時，自己的名字出現在選票上的機會十分渺茫。因此，國安法壓境前夕，民主派初選有更重大的意義&mdash;&mdash;中共拉人封艇並不能將反抗力量趕盡殺絕，而是激起巨大的民意，在七月便率先以公民投票，向國際社會表明香港人真正的意願，無經政權篩選的民意：我們絕不屈服於極權。<br />\n<br />\n因此，在極為艱難的形勢，我們更加沒有退縮的理由。不論此後面對的政治風險以致人身安危有多不明朗，我仍然希望盡所有能力，在中共國安法壓境之際，為街頭線、議會線、國際線增加認受性，取得最大的民意授權。同時，投入國際戰線抗爭的參選人獲得越多選票，他日中共圖謀清算時，將要面對更龐大國際壓力和成本。<br />\n<br />\n我是黃之鋒，經已宣佈參與九龍東立法會的民主派初選，懇請各位一起量化支持國際戰線的民意。當拉人封艇以至送中受審不再是空談，為著延續國際線的血脈，我們很需要香港人的每一票，反制中共消滅香港。<br />\n<br />\n[黃之鋒參選宣言]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/3083967831695704\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fposts%2F3083967831695704&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=a3b67c82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/3083967831695704</a><br />\n<br />\n[At this historical juncture, I, Joshua Wong, will run in the Legislative Council Election.]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/3084331641659323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fposts%2F3084331641659323&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=a064bad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/posts/3084331641659323</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n不屈火苗 存亡號召 Ballot, or Bullet<br />\n#黃之鋒 ‧ 觀塘願景 - 梁凱晴 Jannelle R. Leung ‧ 九東街站要人： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/AntiNSLVolunteer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FAntiNSLVolunteer&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=8d951c57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/AntiNSLVolunteer</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n🎥 <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/香港眾志Demosisto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97Demosisto&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=ce40060e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/香港眾志Demosisto</a><br />\n📷 <a href=\"http://instagram.com/joshua1013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fjoshua1013&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=bc3edc23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://instagram.com/joshua1013</a><br />\n📱 <a href=\"http://t.me/DemosistoOfficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDemosistoOfficial&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=15012436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/DemosistoOfficial</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16601177e56e4ccef207af0b2fa95c1b3fff4874","tid":2081479,"uid":153151,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Xz0C0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Xz0C0n.jpg&h=7b7d0741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誠懇呼籲唔好再舉美國旗，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋支旗，美國人會好反感<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/djateT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/djateT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b683d1c3dfc7bd7b55cfe03978709b0ec2910b75","tid":2081479,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"G Chi Gphone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}